span>Ultra-IAM</span>）的开发与维护，<span>4A</span>即身份管理解决方案是集账号管理、授权管理、认证管理和综合审计、安全访问控制（单点登录）于一体的综合解决方案。</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:17px;font-family:宋体\">主要工作经历：</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:   宋体\">项目名称：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">“金安”工程项目综合运维管理平台统一用户管理系统<span>(2011.01</span>—<span>2011.11)</span></span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:   宋体\">项目描述：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">该系统主要对人员和组织机构信息管理并通过<span>webservice</span>接口推送给各个应用，对资源（<span>Windows</span>，<span>Unix</span>、网络设备和数据库）和资源帐号进行管理并实现资源的单点登录。</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:   宋体\">开发环境：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:   15px;font-family:宋体\">Myeclipse6.5+Tomcat+Ldap+Oracle</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:   宋体\">项目职责：</span></strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">独自完成产品部署配置、前期需求调研、需求开发和验收文档撰写。主要完成的需求：资源驱动开发、<span>Webservice</span>接入调试、人员和组织机构属性修改和导出功能。</span></p><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:   宋体\">其他工作内容<span>:</span></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin-left: 28px\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">1.<span style=\"font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">2010</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">年<span>6</span>月独立完成中国人民银行演示环境<span>4A</span>产品的部署，主要在<span>linux</span>系统部署<span>(Centos + Tomcat + Ldap + &nbsp; Postgre)</span>以及公司相关产品；</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 28px\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">2.<span style=\"font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">2010</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">年<span>8</span>月到<span>10</span>月 独自在重庆移动安全管控项目负责<span>4A</span>产品<span>B/S</span>和<span>C/S</span>应用资源的接入工作，主要完成通过<span>webservice</span>接口同步账号、页面表单代填，<span>AutoIt</span>实现单点登录等工作；</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 28px\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">3.<span style=\"font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">2010</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">年<span>9</span>月到<span>11</span>月负责堡垒主机研发阶段测试（主要对其关键功能<span>sshd</span>、<span>telnet</span>协议登陆资源和<span>CPU</span>、内存占用等性能等测试）并独自完成<span>Vmware ESX</span>硬虚拟环境的部署（<span>vSphere Client</span>和<span>vCenter Server</span>搭建虚拟机）</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 28px\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">4.<span style=\"font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">2010</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">年<span>12</span>月，开发培训</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 56px\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">1)<span style=\"font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">Java</span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">编程规范和产品开发规范学习。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 56px\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">2)<span style=\"font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:   宋体\">界面开发（<span>GT-Grid</span>）：<span>GT-grid</span>组件学习和产品列表模块开发。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 56px\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">3)<span style=\"font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:   宋体\">资源驱动开发（<span>telnet</span>和<span>ssh</span>模拟登陆：<span>Windows</span>和<span>Unix</span>资源帐号获取和增删改操作。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 56px\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">4)<span style=\"font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:   宋体\">单点登录（<span>Autoit3</span>）和接口规范（<span>Token</span>）实现单点登陆：<span>C/S</span>客户端模拟代填和<span>B/S</span>表单代填。</span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 56px\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">5)<span style=\"font-stretch: normal;font-size: 9px;line-height: normal;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:   宋体\">帐号<span>webservice</span>接口：帐号获取和推送以及应用接入。</span></p></td></tr><tr style=\";height:15px\"><td width=\"728\" colspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 728px;border-style: none groove groove;border-right-color: windowtext;border-bottom-color: windowtext;border-left-color: windowtext;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;padding: 0 7px;height: 15px;background: rgb(204, 204, 204)\"><p><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:幼圆\">自我评价</span></strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\";height:73px\"><td width=\"728\" colspan=\"4\" valign=\"top\" style=\"width: 728px;border-style: none groove groove;border-right-color: windowtext;border-bottom-color: windowtext;border-left-color: windowtext;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-left-width: 3px;padding: 0 7px;height: 73px\"><p style=\"text-indent: 31px\"><span style=\"font-size:15px;font-family:宋体\">在工作期间，本人独立积极的完成上级领导分派的任务，在业余时间主动学习。并能够有效的利用所学知识，高效的完成工作内容；本人适应能力和团体协作能力强，能恪守以大局为重的原则，愿意服从集体利益的需要。</span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>', '18', '0', '11', '1', '1', '20', null, '2015-02-16', '系统管理员', null, null, '2015-02-16 16:26:28', '2015-02-16', '1');
